        public SparkParquetWriter​(boolean useIAM,

        Create a SparkParquetWriter that can write to either file or cos URIs
        Parameters:
        isCOS - whether to use IBM Cloud Identity and Access Management; if false we use "HMAC" auth
        cosEndpoint - the S3 endpoint to connect to; include the scheme, typically "https://")
        apiKeyOrAccessKey - a valid ServiceCredential ApiKey (for IAM) or AccessKey (for HMAC)
        serviceInstanceIdOrSecretKey - a valid ServiceInstanceId (for IAM) or SecretKey (for HMAC)
